{
  "stem": "18450.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 267.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were till-- till '41.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's-- is-- [INAUDIBLE] that's the 22nd of June the Germans invaded Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It changed the things that food wasn't as it was before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to stay in line for everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was just like temporary, everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to Russian school, which I learned a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to learn how to [? speak ?].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I wanted to go, and I went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an Institute.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I don't remember even, like in a laboratory, to be a-- to work in a laboratory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the summer, already, the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- but I went to learn the-- the language a little.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was mostly Ukrainian that they taught us, two things, Ukrainian and Russian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never learned the Ukrainian, but Russian, I learned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where were the troops garrisoned?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean, the troops?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- they were on Kostopol, they had barracks there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Would you know, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know they used to take and they had like a public bath.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they used to take them every day another-- used to march to the bathtubs, you know, to take a bath.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure, they had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They marched in the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you were comfortable with the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They made you comfortable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, absolutely no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made you comfortable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to trade, you know, buy some things to send home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were a lot of Russian Jews who were in the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were in the-- the higher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So like Saturday, Sunday, they used to come and look for Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, I mean, they were very friendly, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of them--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
